description: Five-time GRAMMY winner, American jazz bass virtuoso is performing as his alter ego, DJ Brother Mister, at benefit event in NJ, Feb 10, 2018. As DJ Brother Mister, McBride will spin classic R&B, soul and funk records and play along with his bass, making this unique experience one you won’t want to miss.
fulltitle: Christian McBride Chats About Jazz House Kids Event Feb 10, 2018
title: Christian McBride Chats About Jazz House Kids Event Feb 10, 2018
